OL,3,CMerseyside town to honour Nuremberg
OL,4,Ctrials prosecutor on Holocaust
OL,5,CMemorial Day
OL,7,FThe UK's chief prosecutor at the
OL,8,FNuremberg trials of Nazi leaders is to
OL,9,Fbe honoured in the town where he was
OL,10,Fonce the MP.
OL,12,FA blue plaque will be unveiled to Lord
OL,13,FShawcross at St Helens Town Hall, in
OL,14,FMerseyside, after a ceremony to mark
OL,15,FHolocaust Memorial Day.
OL,17,FSir Hartley Shawcross, as he was known
OL,18,Fback then, represented the town in
OL,19,Fparliament from 1945 to 1958.
