OL,7,FThe Labour MP became Attorney General
OL,8,Funder the post-war Attlee government
OL,9,Fand was then appointed as the nation's
OL,10,Fchief prosecutor for the trials.
OL,12,FHe is perhaps best remembered for a
OL,13,Fsingle sentence he said at Nuremberg:
OL,14,F"There comes a point when a man must
OL,15,Frefuse to answer to his leader if he
OL,16,Fis also to answer to his own
OL,17,Fconscience."
OL,19,FLord Shawcross died in 2003, aged 101.
