OL,5,CMemorial Day
OL,7,FVictims of the Holocaust are
OL,8,Fremembered each year on January 27 -
OL,9,Fthe anniversary of the liberation of
OL,10,FAuschwitz-Birkenau, the largest Nazi
OL,11,Fdeath camp. This year is the 80th
OL,12,Fanniversary of the camp's liberation.
OL,14,FThe day is also used to remember the
OL,15,Fmillions killed in subsequent
OL,16,Fgenocides in Cambodia, Rwanda, Bosnia
OL,17,Fand Darfur.
